'''珀拉斯凯縣'''（{{lang en|'''Pulaski County'''}}）是[[美國|美國]][[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]中部的一個縣，面積2,092平方公里。根據[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]估計，本縣共有人口361,474人，是州中人口最多的縣份。<ref name="NACO">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Template.cfm?Section=Find_a_County&Template=/cffiles/counties/state.cfm&state.cfm&statecode=AR|title=NACo - Find a county|author=National Association of Counties|accessdate=2007-04-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071025112518/http://www.naco.org/Template.cfm?Section=Find_a_County&Template=%2Fcffiles%2Fcounties%2Fstate.cfm&state.cfm&statecode=AR|archivedate=2007-10-25}}</ref>本縣的縣治為阿肯色州州府兼最大城市[[小岩城_(阿肯色州)|小石城]]（Little Rock）。{{GR|6}}

珀拉斯凯縣是小石城-[[北小岩城_(阿肯色州)|北小石城]]-[[康威_(阿肯色州)|康威]][[小石城-北小石城-康威大都市統計區|大都會統計區]]的核心部份，而該大都會統計區於2010年共有人口699,757人。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2007/CBSA-EST2007-01.csv | title = Annual Estimates of the Population of Metropolitan and Micropolitan Statistical Areas: April 1, 2000 to July 1, 2008 (CBSA-EST2007-01) | format = [[comma-separated_values|CSV]] | work = 2008 Population Estimates | publisher = [[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]], Population Division | date = 2008-03-27 | accessdate = 2008-03-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080912170654/http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2007/CBSA-EST2007-01.csv | archive-date = 2008-09-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

==歷史==
[[File:Little_Rock.jpg|left]]
本縣於1818年12月15日成立，是阿肯色州第五個成立的縣份，亦是該州第二批成立的三個縣之一。隨同本縣成立的縣份包括[[克拉克縣_(阿肯色州)|克拉克縣]]和[[亨普斯特德縣|亨普斯特德縣]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hearthstonelegacy.com/pulaski_county_arkansas.htm |title=Pulaski County Arkansas Genealogy, History, maps |access-date=2013-09-07 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211232716/http://www.hearthstonelegacy.com/pulaski_county_arkansas.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本縣縣名紀念在[[美國獨立戰爭|美國獨立戰爭]]中戰死的[[波蘭|波蘭]]志願者[[卡西米爾·普瓦斯基|卡西米爾·普瓦斯基]]。{{GR|3}}

於1863年[[美國內戰|美國內戰]]期間，南北兩國軍隊在普瓦斯基縣爆發了貝尤富什戰役（Battle of Bayou Fourche），最終北方獲勝。<ref>“‘The Sting of Being an Exile’: The Little Rock Campaign of 1863. Pulaski County Historical Review 61 (Spring 2013): 34–47.</ref>於1928年開幕的柳樹泉水上樂園（Willow Springs Water Park）亦位於本縣內。該水上樂園是美國其中一個最具歷史的水上樂園。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://lasr.net/pages/city.php?Little%20Rock&Arkansas&City_ID=AR0203012&VA=Y&Attraction_ID=AR0203012a012 |title=Willow Springs Water Park - Little Rock, Arkansas |publisher=Lasr.net |date= |accessdate=2013-07-27 |archive-date=2016-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313201151/http://lasr.net/pages/city.php?arkansas&attraction_id=ar0203012a012&city_id=ar0203012&little%20rock&va=y |dead-url=no }}</ref>

